{
 "name": "RPlog_Justice",
 "title": "Justice",
 "summary": "In Caspar SandBar, the cold Bureau of Operations officer Joir -- flanked by two bodyguards after a recent shooting -- seeks out the Marine pilot Tarlin Lathis to discuss the wounded Ambassador and the investigation surrounding the attack. Over coffee poured by the bartender Ariani, the two men trade guarded, probing words; Tarlin presses for the Ambassador medical status and bristles at what he takes for a veiled threat, which Joir denies. Each pledges to share any information in pursuit of justice, and the encounter closes with both men solemnly echoing the same indoctrinated creeds -- Justice indeed and Duty First -- as patrons like the Quarren Ressec and a wary Clarise drift through the bar.",
